<div class='container'>
  <h3>Weely Student Birthday Report</h3>
  <p>
    Below is a list of Student Birthdays that will take place within the
    next week. This message is auto-generated on the server by calculating
    what the date will be one week from today and returning any students who's
    birthdays will take place between today and the calculated date. Please be
    aware that some discrepencies may take place due to overlapping dates,
    improper dates being stored for each student, and other issues that arrise
    when creating the students records. If errors are found, please contact the
    site administrator via e-mail, as soon as possible, so they can be fixed.
  </p>
  <table class='table'>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Student Name</th>
        <th>Birthday</th>
        <th>Age</th>
        <th>Day to B-Day</th>
        <th>Belt</th>
        <th>Level</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <% unless @students.empty? %>
      <% @students.each do |student| %>
        <tr>
          <td><%=student.last%>,&nbsp;<%=student.first%></td>
          <td><%=student.birthday%></td>
          <td><%=student.current_age%></td>
          <td><%=student.days_left%></td>
          <td><%=student.belt.capitalize%></td>
          <td><%=student.level%></td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <tr>
        <td colspan='6'>
          No Students will have a Birthday within the next month!
        </td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
